tags.description: Fireman's Beach features a beach (no dogs), marina, picnic areas, a covered pavilion, and a playground.  There is an easy walking path within park boundaries to nearby Ice House Park.  Parking is free on weekdays and there is a parking fee on weekends.
tags.name: Fireman's Beach

tags.description: A sanctuary for migrating birds.  Birders can view over 200 different species here throughout the year.
tags.name: Collins Bird Sanctuary
